

pause()                COHERENT System Call               pause()




Wait for signal

iinntt ppaauussee()

pause  suspends execution  until the  process receives  a signal.
The  awaited signal  could  come from  kill, alarm,  or the  con-
trolling terminal.

***** See Also *****

alarm, COHERENT system calls, kill, signal(), sleep()













































